#	pdfkit --> converting html to pdf
#   	to install, execute the following:
#			apt-get install python-pip
#			pip install pdfkit
# 			apt-get install wkhtmltopdf
#		to use pdfkit with python 3 it might be necessary to execute the following:
#			cp -r /usr/local/lib/python2.x/dist-packages/pdfkit /usr/local/lib/python3.x/dist-packages/pdfkit
#		or
#			cp -r /home/user/.local/lib/python2.x/site-packages/pdfkit /usr/local/lib/python3.x/dist-packages/pdfkt
#